 BABYMONSTER 在最新单曲“Stuck in the Middle”中尝试新声音https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-new-single-stuck-in-the-middle-3564422?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=babymonster-new-single-stuck-in-the-middlePuah Ziwei Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:17:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3564422 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它被描述为“不是嘻哈曲目”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-new-single-stuck-in-the-middle-3564422">BABYMONSTER 在最新单曲“Stuck in the Middle”中尝试新的声音后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新秀韩国流行女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babymonster">BABYMONSTER</a>发布了她们的新单曲《Stuck in the Middle》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/babymonster-batter-up-review-swing-and-a-miss-3549523">BABYMONSTER 备受期待的首张专辑“Batter Up”是一次摇摆和失败</a></strong></li></ul><p>在完全用英语演唱的新单曲中，BABYMONSTER 尝试了新的钢琴民谣声音。这首歌显然是该女子组合的一个新方向，该女子组合于 2023 年 11 月首次亮相<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-swing-for-the-big-leagues-on-debut-single-batter-up-3549426">，推出了首张单曲“Batter Up”</a> ，这是一首嘻哈风格的流行歌曲。</p><p>与此同时，《Stuck in the Middle》的音乐录影带中，女团在宇宙中央的一座大宅邸中表演了这首歌。 <em>“哦，孩子，你让我真的很困惑/不知道我应该做什么/我和你夹在中间，”</em>他们唱道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="BABYMONSTER - &#39;Stuck In The Middle&#39; M/V" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GsV1i0QHi-o?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Stuck in the Middle》最初是由女子组合签约的 YG Entertainment 创始人梁贤淑于 2023 年除夕夜（12 月 31 日）宣布的。当时，杨形容这首歌“不是嘻哈歌曲”。 “这对我来说太新鲜了，我想知道 YG [娱乐] 是否曾经发行过这样的歌曲，”他补充道。</p><p> “如果要分享我个人的看法，每当我听这首歌时，我都会闭上眼睛，感觉就像处于外太空零重力的状态，”杨继续谈到BABYMONSTER的新歌。</p><p> “成员们声音的技巧和独特的色彩让我想要专注于哪怕是最微小的呼吸，”他补充道。 “这让我在聆听时集中注意力。我认为这是一首可以用‘美丽’来形容的歌曲。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="BABYMONSTER 下一阶段 | YG公告" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3piGcUtxBD0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时，BABYMONSTER 的第七位成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-ahyeon-rejoin-group-after-missing-their-debut-3576638">Ahyeon 将在四月发行首张专辑时重新加入女团</a>。这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-final-line-up-include-all-seven-members-3442308">最初是BABYMONSTER阵容中的一员</a>，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yg-entertainment-trainee-ahyeon-no-longer-debut-babymonster-health-reasons-3539693">由于“健康原因”不得不推迟出道</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-new-single-stuck-in-the-middle-3564422">BABYMONSTER 在最新单曲“Stuck in the Middle”中尝试新的声音后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
